  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Your goal.</strong></h2>Run and survive the onslaught of the Ayaards.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931200/extras/424fcf10e8a6ff81e22c5843155d44bf.poster.avif?t=1683030883\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931200/extras/424fcf10e8a6ff81e22c5843155d44bf.webm?t=1683030883\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931200/extras/424fcf10e8a6ff81e22c5843155d44bf.mp4?t=1683030883\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Use your rewards to grow stronger, buy food and equipment.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931200/extras/9d0f1314ce52e50faf0efe12b053a170.poster.avif?t=1683030883\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931200/extras/9d0f1314ce52e50faf0efe12b053a170.webm?t=1683030883\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931200/extras/9d0f1314ce52e50faf0efe12b053a170.mp4?t=1683030883\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Travel from statue to statue and try to escape.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931200/extras/8354931bc2e939ab7be347bc57e19ee8.poster.avif?t=1683030883\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931200/extras/8354931bc2e939ab7be347bc57e19ee8.webm?t=1683030883\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931200/extras/8354931bc2e939ab7be347bc57e19ee8.mp4?t=1683030883\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>What to expect.</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Chaotic exhilarating fast-paced combat. With a hint of careful planning.<br></li><li>Multiple different enemies with unique movesets to conquer.<br></li><li>Plentifull of bosses to catch you off guard.<br></li><li>Level up, buy food, equipment and tools in order to conquer more ground.<br></li><li>Find out the mysteries of the underground and help everyone escape.<br></li><li>Easy to pick up. Hard to master.<br></li><li>Provides a good challenge.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Your goal.</strong></h2>Run and survive the onslaught of the Ayaards.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931200/extras/424fcf10e8a6ff81e22c5843155d44bf.poster.avif?t=1683030883\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931200/extras/424fcf10e8a6ff81e22c5843155d44bf.webm?t=1683030883\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931200/extras/424fcf10e8a6ff81e22c5843155d44bf.mp4?t=1683030883\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Use your rewards to grow stronger, buy food and equipment.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931200/extras/9d0f1314ce52e50faf0efe12b053a170.poster.avif?t=1683030883\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931200/extras/9d0f1314ce52e50faf0efe12b053a170.webm?t=1683030883\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931200/extras/9d0f1314ce52e50faf0efe12b053a170.mp4?t=1683030883\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Travel from statue to statue and try to escape.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931200/extras/8354931bc2e939ab7be347bc57e19ee8.poster.avif?t=1683030883\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931200/extras/8354931bc2e939ab7be347bc57e19ee8.webm?t=1683030883\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931200/extras/8354931bc2e939ab7be347bc57e19ee8.mp4?t=1683030883\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>What to expect.</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Chaotic exhilarating fast-paced combat. With a hint of careful planning.<br></li><li>Multiple different enemies with unique movesets to conquer.<br></li><li>Plentifull of bosses to catch you off guard.<br></li><li>Level up, buy food, equipment and tools in order to conquer more ground.<br></li><li>Find out the mysteries of the underground and help everyone escape.<br></li><li>Easy to pick up. Hard to master.<br></li><li>Provides a good challenge.</li></ul>",
